title: Episode 229: Everybody's Dookied Themselves Before (Feat. Lil Mo & Passport Cutty)
itunes:title: Episode 229: Everybody's Dookied Themselves Before (Feat. Lil Mo & Passport Cutty)
description:
Singer Lil Mo joins the ladies of Lip Service for their first studio recording of 2020. The ladies begin a new segment called "Ful Disclosure" which entails each person to share a humiliating story (Passport Cutty takes the cake with this one). The ladies discuss the pros and cons of living with your partner before marriage, ideal proposals, and much more. Enjoy!
